---
title: Quick Basil Pesto & Pork Fusilli with Apple Salad & Parmesan
description: In this dish, we've teamed rich basil pesto with a silky cream-based sauce, then followed it up with tender pork mince for a meal
that looks and smells every bit as good as it tastes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-basil-pesto-pork-fusilli-0c53db04.jpg
